  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201310/76d28d9e0fb84a20ba7c7b5587c1472e.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>Robin老师带你聊美容学英文</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t时间: 10月22日（星期二）16:00 - 17:00<br />\n\t主讲老师:<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/21958373\" target=\"_blank\">罗宾</a></span><br />\n\t公开课地点: O+口语大厅（<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载CCTalk</a>）</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178,34,34);\"><strong>视频回顾</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178,34,34);\"><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>课堂内容提要</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>1.<span style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serief; line-height: 22px;\">罗宾老师聊个人护理</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t（1）skincare</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; facial cleanser</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; facial scrub</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; toner</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; facial cream/lotion/moisturiser</p>\n<p>\n\t（2）make-up</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; foundation</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; face powder</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; eyeliner</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; eye shadow</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; mascara</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; lipstick/lip gloss</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>2.Cosmetic surgery&mdash;Q&amp;A 听力与词汇讲解</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>3.Exercise</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>4.课后答疑</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">想提前一周知道最精彩的公开课安排吗？那就来订阅沪江CCTalk电子报吧！<a href=\"http://app.hujiang.com/mail/sub/72/\" target=\"_blank\">电子报的订阅入口&gt;&gt;</a></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">沪江网校还为大家提供了其他的活动，欢迎大家预约：<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/gongkaike/\" target=\"_blank\">最新活动预约</a></span></p>\n<div id=\"article\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">\n\t<p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t<strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201209/58f013100fe44857a846c5c5aef19325.gif\" style=\"marg